### Third-Party Open Source Components

This project utilizes several third-party libraries and tools. Their respective licenses are listed below:

1. **Streamlit** (https://github.com/streamlit/streamlit)
   - License: Apache License 2.0
   - Purpose: Frontend & UI development framework

2. **LangChain** (https://github.com/langchain-ai/langchain)
   - License: MIT License
   - Purpose: LLM Orchestration & Prompt Chaining

3. **Mermaid.js** (https://github.com/mermaid-js/mermaid)
   - License: MIT License
   - Purpose: ERD & Flowchart Diagram rendering

4. **Faker** (https://github.com/joke2k/faker)
   - License: MIT License
   - Purpose: Korean/English synthetic dummy data generation

5. **PyMySQL** (https://github.com/PyMySQL/PyMySQL)
   - License: MIT License
   - Purpose: Pure-Python MySQL client driver for SQLAlchemy
